    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Superfamily Portunoidea Rafinesque, 1815, dorsal habitus: A, Achelous anceps (de Saussure, 1857), male, cw 30.5 mm (BLSZ 271); B, Achelous sebae (H. Milne Edwards, 1834), female, cw 56.6 mm (BLSZ 245); C, Achelous ventralis (A. Milne-Edwards, 1879), male, cw 29.1 mm (BLSZ 185); D, Callinectes marginatus (A. Milne-Edwards, 1861), female, cw 81.8 mm (BLSZ 057); E, juvenile specimen of Callinectes marginatus, cw 20.0 mm (BLSZ 230). Scale bars: 20 mm." ;
